  <brief_title>Coordinated Assessment of Notifications of Trials Containing Overt Published Errors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of Response of Medical Journal Editorial Boards to Notification of Serious Discrepancies in Published Clinical Trials in Human Patients.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
